{"trip_id":"2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque","epigraph":{"quote":"Then there was a long, peaceful silence + we walked out at 7."},"moments":[{"seq":2,"place_id":"stalisfield-kent-uk","lon":0.812558,"lat":51.2442782,"place":"Stalisfield, Kent, UK","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"6.15 We've reached Stalisfield + changed supper booking from 8.15 to 7.30. Sunshine.","images":[]},{"seq":3,"place_id":"dover","lon":1.3266,"lat":51.1264,"place":"Dover","date":"2019-06-06","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"Horrid crossing. Delayed only one hour in the end. The French being extra thorough.","images":[]},{"seq":5,"place_id":"gray-france","lon":5.5919867,"lat":47.4455642,"place":"Gray, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"We had a good lunch at a restaurant by a river in Gray which Simon had visited twice before with Charles.","images":[]},{"seq":6,"place_id":"pesmes-france","lon":5.56743,"lat":47.2796,"place":"Pesmes, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Pesmes a very pretty town with winding streets + the remains of a Roman layout at the top.","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0321_R_1.webp","w":790,"h":900,"caption":"Notre-Dame de Gray Basilica","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0321_R_2.webp","w":900,"h":478,"caption":"View from our campsite, across the river at Pesmes on R. Ognion","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0322_L_1.webp","w":390,"h":773,"caption":"Porte St-Hilaire","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":7,"place_id":"saline-royale-arc-et-senans-france","lon":5.777332,"lat":47.0339828,"place":"Saline Royale, Arc-et-Senans, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"They piped salty water from the original site to the new factory, 13k as crow flies but 33 k of 2 underground wood pipes","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0322_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":519,"caption":"PATRIMOINE MONDIAL DE L'UNESCO — Saline Royale","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0322_R_2.webp","w":900,"h":456,"caption":"Saline Royale site plan with handwritten annotations","type":"map"}]},{"seq":8,"place_id":"meyrieu-les-etangs-france","lon":5.19121,"lat":45.5125,"place":"Meyrieu-les-Étangs, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"I had a good shower.","images":[]},{"seq":9,"place_id":"malaucene-france","lon":5.1321258,"lat":44.1732744,"place":"Malaucène, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"SUNSHINE. Hooray! Our van is in shade in the morning, so it's a bit chilly. But we now need the shade in the afternoon.","images":[]},{"seq":10,"place_id":"villes-sur-auzon-france","lon":5.2338492,"lat":44.0582508,"place":"Villes-sur-Auzon, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"transit_stop","quote":"We bought cakes + cherries. Lots of cherry trees with fruit.","images":[]},{"seq":11,"place_id":"gorges-de-la-nesque-france","lon":5.2857202,"lat":44.0481646,"place":"Gorges de la Nesque, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"1/4 Grand Canyon but small + green + practically no houses. Caves, water patterns in rock.","images":[]},{"seq":12,"place_id":"gordes-france","lon":5.2002043,"lat":43.9110641,"place":"Gordes, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"by the 1940s the town was nearly abandoned. Then artists came. It's now a beautiful town","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0325_L_1.webp","w":715,"h":900,"caption":"L'abbaye de Sénanque","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":13,"place_id":"saint-pantaleon-vaucluse-france","lon":5.2155788,"lat":43.8812622,"place":"Saint-Pantaléon, Vaucluse, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"transit_stop","quote":"The French even have a St. Trousers. St Pantaleon.","images":[]},{"seq":14,"place_id":"la-verdiere-france","lon":5.9348456,"lat":43.6379633,"place":"La Verdière, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The campsite served coq au vin. A big party came in + sat at a long table. A flock of sheep went past.","images":[]},{"seq":15,"place_id":"barjols-france","lon":6.0056803,"lat":43.558133,"place":"Barjols, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"It's very attractive + has at least 30 drinking fountains.","images":[]},{"seq":16,"place_id":"cotignac-france","lon":6.1502672,"lat":43.5280531,"place":"Cotignac, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Blisteringly hot. Washing dried fast.","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0326_L_1.webp","w":491,"h":531,"caption":"Troglodite rock houses","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0326_L_2.webp","w":491,"h":531,"caption":"olive preszes with ratchets","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0326_R_1.webp","w":824,"h":741,"caption":"Abbey Le Thoronet.","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"la-garde-freinet-france","lon":6.4687979,"lat":43.3196859,"place":"La Garde-Freinet, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"a lovely Mediaeval Village. V. Good wine shop Le Cellier run by Hervé Sauvage.","images":[]},{"seq":19,"place_id":"plan-de-la-tour-france","lon":6.54537,"lat":43.3384,"place":"Plan-de-la-Tour, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Then we came down down down the hills to Plan de la Tour.","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0327_L_1.webp","w":680,"h":900,"caption":"Le Thoronet abbey interior and cloister","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":20,"place_id":"saint-tropez-france","lon":6.6405225,"lat":43.2727191,"place":"Saint-Tropez, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"transit_stop","quote":"soon joined a ghastly queue going into St. Tropez.","images":[]},{"seq":21,"place_id":"domaine-du-rayol-le-rayol-canadel-sur-mer-france","lon":6.4842507,"lat":43.1543384,"place":"Domaine du Rayol, Le Rayol-Canadel-sur-Mer, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"a Mediterranean garden which has collected plants from hot places all over the world.","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0327_R_1.webp","w":436,"h":386,"caption":"view of sea from cafe","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0327_R_2.webp","w":836,"h":499,"caption":"NZ Eucalyptus garden trees","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":22,"place_id":"near-aix-en-provence-france-unnamed-thursday-night-camp","lon":1.8883335,"lat":46.603354,"place":"Near Aix-en-Provence, France (unnamed Thursday-night camp)","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The boars trot along with their tails straight up in the air.","images":[]},{"seq":23,"place_id":"aix-en-provence-france","lon":5.4474738,"lat":43.5298424,"place":"Aix-en-Provence, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"Simon took great care to position the van with one wheel on the pavement slanting past a tree.","images":[]},{"seq":24,"place_id":"orange-france","lon":4.8078783,"lat":44.1371311,"place":"Orange, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We spent ages at the Theatre. It could hold 9000 people","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0328_R_1.webp","w":412,"h":419,"caption":"Triumphal Arch, Orange","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0328_R_2.webp","w":461,"h":419,"caption":"Roman Theatre, About O","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0329_L_1.webp","w":886,"h":805,"caption":"Aerial view of Roman theatre stage wall","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":25,"place_id":"eglise-saint-martin-de-laives-laives-france","lon":4.8541139,"lat":46.6389274,"place":"Église Saint-Martin-de-Laives, Laives, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"we went into the cool church + wow, there was a music group there.","images":[]},{"seq":26,"place_id":"laives-france","lon":4.8467143,"lat":46.6452774,"place":"Laives, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We moved out with me still lying in bed to a nice open, sunny view of the lake.","images":[]},{"seq":27,"place_id":"villeneuve-sur-yonne-france","lon":3.2942751,"lat":48.0820102,"place":"Villeneuve-sur-Yonne, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"the campsite is by the river, so I did yoga + then we swam. We read.","images":[]},{"seq":28,"place_id":"amiens-france","lon":2.2956951,"lat":49.8941708,"place":"Amiens, France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We had a good supper by the Somme. Pork stew + apple pud.","images":[]},{"seq":29,"place_id":"noyelles-sur-mer-baie-de-somme-france","lon":1.7074603,"lat":50.1828403,"place":"Noyelles-sur-Mer (Baie de Somme), France","date":"2019-06-06","role":"overnight_base","quote":"A glorious last day in France. The wind was gentle, so we cycled to + from le Crotoy.","images":[{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0332_L_1.webp","w":528,"h":660,"caption":"Intermarché milk supply chain leaflet","type":"ticket"},{"src":"media/2019-france-provence-burgundy-pesmes-malaucene-senanque/B_0332_L_2.webp","w":554,"h":628,"caption":"Intermarché bread supply chain leaflet","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":30,"place_id":"coquelles-eurotunnel","lon":1.8147,"lat":50.9228,"place":"Coquelles (Eurotunnel)","date":"2019-06-06","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"We drove to the Channel Tunnel + followed a handsome Ferrari onto the train.","images":[]},{"seq":31,"place_id":"peter-s-home-england-location-unspecified","lon":-1.4989422,"lat":53.3747215,"place":"Peter's home, England (location unspecified)","date":"2019-06-06","role":"main_stop","quote":"Conrad had spent 2 hours playing football in 30° & gave me a very sweaty hug when I arrived.","images":[]}]}